LED_calibrate = 󰇮(⥌𝘴,𝘳↦󱟱⥌𝐝,cb↦{  󰤱
  © SCENE_CALIB = 󰲡({"fx":[[2,1]],"*":[{"fx":[],"1":[x,0,65280]},{"fx":[],"1":[1001-x,0,16711680]}]});
  © MSG = ‹Is red visible at the end of the LED strip?›;
  
  󱫬 𝐝.config({LEDC:1000});
  © show = 󰲡𝐝.scene(‹calib›,SCENE_CALIB(x),✗,󷰾);
  
  ⎉ 𝔖 = [[1,100,1000]];
  ➰(✓) { ⎉ [l,m,h] = 𝔖􋕛(󷰾);
         󱫬 show(m)
